title: Act4_Judge_N0
---
/// no repeat
<<set_portrait YarnManager Judge>>
The Judge: What a twist!
The Judge: Well, at least now you know who to kill! The rest of your mission should be easy~

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: I...

<<set_portrait YarnManager Judge>>
The Judge: Don’t act so surprised. You’ve been suspecting her for a while, haven’t you?

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: I didn’t want it to be true.

<<set_portrait YarnManager Judge>>
The Judge: Boohoo! Now that you have evidence, what’s stopping you?
The Judge: I suppose I have the Fate Exchanger to thank for speeding things along.

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: You know him?

<<set_portrait YarnManager Judge>>
The Judge: In a way. He’s another spiritual being, works for the Devil Arcana.
The Judge: Spends all day sneaking between worlds and messing with mortals. Likes to tempt them, bring out their dark side.

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: A dark side?

<<set_portrait YarnManager Judge>>
The Judge: I know, you’re much too boring to have a dark side.
The Judge: But I swear, he always waits until my back is turned to show up.

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: [i]Never mind that. Eve is still...[/i]

<<set_portrait YarnManager Judge>>
The Judge: Alright, yaddah yaddah this is your sacred duty, blah blah Prism needs its enforcer. You know the drill.

<<player_respawn YarnManager>>
===


title: Act4_Decisions_P4N1
---
<<set_portrait YarnManager Eve>>
Eve: Hey, are you okay?

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: [i]If I kill her before the Hierophant can ever possess her, it’ll stop the Assimilation.[/i]
Cyrus: [i]This would be the end, wouldn’t it? Just as the Judge said. True justice will be brought to the world.[/i]
Cyrus: [i]But...[/i]

<<set_portrait YarnManager Eve>>
Eve: Umm, hello? Can you hear me? Are you okay?

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: ...Yes, I can hear you.

<<set_portrait YarnManager Eve>>
Eve: Oh, that’s great! I was worried that you hit your head or something when I found you. I'm Eve!
Eve: What’s your name?

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: [i]Maybe I should spend some more time understanding who “Eve” really is.[/i]

<<clear_portrait YarnManager>>
: [i]The two return to town.[/i]

<<set_portrait YarnManager Eve>>
Eve: We make a great dispatcher-hunter, duo, don’t we? Took those monsters out like it was nothing!

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: Eve...

