title: Act4_LunaSearch_DoNothing
---
<<set_route YarnManager LunaSearch_DoNothing>>

<<set_portrait YarnManager Officer>>
Officer: (muffled) Captain! We have a situation!

<<set_portrait YarnManager Luna>>
Luna: Let’s move.

<<set_portrait YarnManager Eve>>
Eve: Ugh, the signals are all messed up. I can’t reach him. Who was at the door?

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: Oh, I think they got the wrong place. They left.

<<set_portrait YarnManager Eve>>
Eve: Huh, strange.
Eve: I'll see if I can get in contact with anyone else... The Hunter agencies haven't said anything either.
Eve: Ugh, I just feel useless right now.

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: What more can you do?

<<set_portrait YarnManager Eve>>
Eve: I don’t know, but hiding instead of going out there and doing something makes me feel like a coward.

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: Doesn't that make us all cowards, then?

<<set_portrait YarnManager Eve>>
Eve: Oh, no, I didn't mean it like- I’m just scared.

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: Of course you are, it’s an emergency. Best thing to do is just follow instructions.

<<set_portrait YarnManager Eve>>
Eve: But you don't seem fazed at all.

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: Well...
Cyrus: [i]I wouldn't say I'm normal.[/i]

<<set_portrait YarnManager Eve>>
Eve: Cyrus...
Eve: I don’t know if my dispatcher broke, but it looks like it’s detecting meminiscors in the city.

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: Send me the locations, I'll take care of it. Remember to lock your doors.

<<set_portrait YarnManager Eve>>
Eve: Here. Be careful and report to me!
===


